description:
House Rules Series 3 Episode 1

Melbourne lovers Bronik and Corrine are the first team to hand over their house keys to the competition. Their opposition have just seven days to completely transform their home before judging. They are each given a work zone within the house and a set budget, and must impress judges Joe Snell and Wendy Moore as well as the homeowners by week's end. Will the competing teams hit or miss the mark? And will they finish their zone by deadline?
